(38, 1000, 'available', 3, 9.9, 36000, 46692, 'Thinking for a splendid wedding function of your offspring (s)? Are you worried for the expenditure of the most desired ceremonial function? Remove your worries! Take a marriage deposit scheme in the name of your offspring. Save a small deposit monthly and have a handsome amount at the end of tenor.<br><br><font color="#ff0000" size="4">Pre tenor encashment benefit:</font><br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; If you need money, you can take loan at the bank’s suitable terms and condition.<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; In case of pre tenor encashment of the scheme, you can still get attractive benefit.<br><br>Contact any one of our branches. You can also apply through online.<br><br><font color="#ff0000" size="4">Condition</font>: Government tax and excise duty are applicable.', ''),
